HB1736
1 promissory note, health-care-insurance receivable, or general intangible, is
2 ineffective to the extent that the term:
3 (1) would impair the creation, attachment, or perfection of a
4 security interest; or
5 (2) provides that the assignment or transfer or the creation,
6 attachment, or perfection of the security interest may give rise to a
7 default, breach, right of recoupment, claim, defense, termination, right of
8 termination, or remedy under the promissory note, health-care-insurance
